				<div class="content">Just another thought for those who have visual impairment....you could make a small notch on the outermost area of the dial to allow for Zero position or a small dot on the actual Dial .... broaden this out to a Braille patterned dial - number of dots adjacent to each finger hole to represent each number.....(epoxy maybe)<br>
<br>
Another possibility would be a ceramic based, glow-in-the-dark material to illuminate what each used feels the need to see....numbers, dial, buttons, etc. ...<br>
<br>
 ***  Enjoy ***  ....;--)<br>
